s-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">There are both mens and womens sizes as well as hoodies, v-necks and triblends available. </span><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\" /><br style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\" /><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">Order now and if this campaign is funded we expect the shirts to arrive approximately when ROS </span><span class=\"il\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">Kinetic Kame is</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"> released. The </span><a style=\"color: #1155cc; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\" href=\"http://bit.ly/KinteicKame\" target=\"_blank\">campaign</a><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"> closes on May 9th don\'t wait too long to order. </span>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\"> </span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\">Here\'s a high resolution version of the Kinetic logo. </span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.8px;\"> </span></span></div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.ros.org/news/assets_c/2016/04/kinetic-1441.html\"><img class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\" src=\"http://www.ros.org/news/assets_c/2016/04/kinetic-thumb-640x530-1441.png\" alt=\"kinetic.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"530\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Note that we have two providers one in the US and one in Europe. The main link: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/KinteicKame\">http://bit.ly/KinteicKame</a> redirects based on your IP address. If you want to access the individual 